title: Hanjin Shipping - number of TEUs 2016
summary: This is a grouped bar chart showing Number of TEUs on the Y-axis throughout 8 Months for Owned, Chartered, and Orderbook on the X-axis.
All through the Months, the Number of TEUs for Chartered have risen. On the other hand, for Owned the Number of TEUs have decreased.
For Month June 13 2016, Chartered had the highest Number of TEUs 351338.0 among the 3 groups and in July 12 2016, Orderbook had the lowest Number of TEUs 0.0.
Month June 13 2016 and September 7 2016 had the biggest gap of 33088.0 between the highest and lowest Number of TEUs found for Chartered.
